    public interface SpecializableTermReference
extends VocabularyMemberReference
    A representation of the model object 'Specializable Term Reference'. SpecializableTermReference is a reference to a specializable term in some vocabulary, in order to add other specializations to it.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Specializations

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<SpecializationAxiom> getOwnedSpecializations()
        Returns the value of the 'Owned Specializations' containment reference list. The list contents are of type SpecializationAxiom. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Owning Reference'. The set of specialization axioms added to the referenced term by this reference
